---
import ThemeToggle from '../components/ThemeToggle.astro';

export const prerender = false;

const currentUser = Astro.locals.user;

if (!currentUser) {
  return Astro.redirect('/login');
}
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>付款方式 - World X Trip</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="查看 World X Trip 的付款方式，并在付款后提交截图与登录邮箱以人工开通会员。"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f8f3f8;
        --bg-soft: #fcf7fc;
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
        --panel-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);

        --text: #20171f;
        --muted: #7d6879;

        --line: rgba(80, 42, 72, 0.1);
        --line-strong: rgba(80, 42, 72, 0.16);

        --accent: #b05c8e;
        --accent-soft: rgba(176, 92, 142, 0.1);

        --shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(113, 61, 104, 0.1);
      }

      :root[data-theme='dark'] {
        --bg: #0c0b14;
        --bg-soft: #131222;
        --panel: rgba(18, 20, 34, 0.78);
        --panel-strong: rgba(24, 27, 46, 0.92);

        --text: #f7f2ff;
        --muted: #b8a8d6;

        --line: rgba(120, 104, 255, 0.18);
        --line-strong: rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.26);

        --accent: #ff4fd8;
        --accent-soft: rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.14);

        --shadow: 0 20px 52px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Noto Serif SC", "Songti SC", "Source Han Serif SC",
          "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(216, 140, 200, 0.14), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(176, 92, 142, 0.1), transparent 26%),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom center, rgba(106, 226, 255, 0.08), transparent 36%),
          var(--bg);
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 24px 24px 88px;
      }

      .topbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .topbar-actions {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .back-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .back-link:hover {
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .hero,
      .section,
      .footer-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: var(--panel);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero {
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 36px 32px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 18px 0 14px;
        font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 56px);
        line-height: 1.1;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .hero p {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 46em;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.95;
        font-size: 17px;
      }

      .layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 420px);
        gap: 24px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .section {
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 26px;
      }

      .section h2 {
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .plan-list,
      .instruction-list,
      .notes-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .plan-item,
      .instruction-item,
      .note-item {
        padding: 16px 18px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: var(--panel-strong);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .plan-item strong,
      .instruction-item strong,
      .note-item strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .plan-item p,
      .instruction-item p,
      .note-item p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      .payment-card {
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 26px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: var(--panel);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        position: sticky;
        top: 24px;
      }

      .payment-card h2 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .payment-card p {
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      .qr-wrap {
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 18px;
        background: var(--panel-strong);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .qr-wrap img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: white;
      }

      .qr-caption {
        margin-top: 14px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 46px;
        padding: 0 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1;
        transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease, color 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .button-primary {
        background: var(--text);
        color: var(--bg);
      }

      .button-primary:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.18), 0 0 20px rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.12);
      }

      .button-secondary {
        border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
        background: transparent;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .footer-card {
        margin-top: 24px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 22px 24px;
      }

      .footer-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      code.inline {
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--panel-strong);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      @media (max-width: 960px) {
        .layout {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .payment-card {
          position: static;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 720px) {
        .container {
          padding: 18px 16px 68px;
        }

        .hero,
        .section,
        .payment-card,
        .footer-card {
          border-radius: 22px;
          padding: 20px 18px;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 32px;
        }

        .section h2,
        .payment-card h2 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="topbar">
        <a class="back-link" href="/pricing">← 返回订阅方案</a>

        <div class="topbar-actions">
          <a class="back-link" href="/account">我的账户</a>
          <ThemeToggle />
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="hero">
        <span class="eyebrow">解锁全部付费内容</span>
        <h1>付款方式与开通说明</h1>
        <p>
          您当前已登录，接下来只需要选择合适的方案并完成付款。
          付款课后请提供支付凭证等信息。等待审核通过后即可解锁付费内容。
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="layout">
        <div style="display:grid; gap:24px;">
          <section class="section">
            <h2>可选方案</h2>

            <div class="plan-list">
              <div class="plan-item">
                <strong>1个月 — $9</strong>
                <p>适合短期集中阅读、旅行前做功课，或先试订一个月。</p>
              </div>

              <div class="plan-item">
                <strong>6个月 — $45</strong>
                <p>适合持续跟踪多个地区更新，整体更均衡，也更能体现更新速度的价值。</p>
              </div>

              <div class="plan-item">
                <strong>1年 — $90</strong>
                <p>适合长期关注完整游记、延伸档案与持续积累的读者。</p>
              </div>

              <div class="plan-item">
                <strong>终生会员 — $130</strong>
                <p>一次开通，长期访问，后续新增付费内容也会持续可见。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="section">
            <h2>付款后请提供这些信息</h2>

            <div class="instruction-list">
              <div class="instruction-item">
                <strong>1. 站内登录邮箱</strong>
                <p>
                  当前登录邮箱是：
                  <code class="inline">{currentUser.email ?? '未读取到邮箱'}</code>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="instruction-item">
                <strong>2. 付款截图</strong>
                <p>请保存付款完成后的截图或凭证，方便核对金额与付款时间。</p>
              </div>

              <div class="instruction-item">
                <strong>3. 购买方案</strong>
                <p>请明确说明你购买的是 1个月、6个月、1年，还是终生会员。</p>
              </div>

              <div class="instruction-item">
                <strong>4. 如付款账户与登录邮箱不同</strong>
                <p>也请一并说明，以免付款记录与站内账号无法对应。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="section">
            <h2>开通与注意事项</h2>

            <div class="notes-list">
              <div class="note-item">
                <strong>审核开通</strong>
                <p>收到付款信息并核对无误后，系统会更新您的会员状态并开通权限。</p>
              </div>

              <div class="note-item">
                <strong>开通时效</strong>
                <p>通常会在看到付款信息后的数小时内完成。若较长时间未开通，可再次提醒。</p>
              </div>

              <div class="note-item">
                <strong>开通后查看位置</strong>
                <p>开通完成后，你可以前往“我的账户”查看会员状态，或直接返回文章页查看是否已解锁全文。</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="actions">
              <a class="button button-secondary" href="/pricing">返回订阅方案</a>
              <a class="button button-primary" href="/account">查看我的账户</a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <aside class="payment-card">
          <h2>扫码付款</h2>
          <p>
            请根据你希望购买的方案金额完成付款。付款完成后，
            按照左侧说明，把登录邮箱、付款截图和购买方案发送邮件至 etnavax56@gmail.com。
          </p>

          <div class="qr-wrap">
            <img src="/images/payment/paypal.png" alt="PayPal 收款二维码" />
            <div class="qr-caption">
              PayPal 收款二维码
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="/pricing">我还想再看看方案</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <footer class="footer-card">
        <p>
          千金难买好时光，与其纠结不如纵狂，呼朋引伴、举杯同乐、销尽万古愁思肠。若得此生常尽兴，不羡长生不羡仙！
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>